To help you with UI analysis and design visuals for your Daily, Monthly, and Yearly Expenditure Tracking App, I’ll break down the project into individual screens based on your earlier request, explain each screen’s purpose, the UI components it should have, and then generate an image for each screen.

🔧 Project Scope Summary
Login / Register with RoomDB

Set Monthly Budget

Add/Delete Expense

Track Daily, Monthly, Yearly Expenses

Display Charts or Lists

Store in Room (future: Firebase/server)

🧩 Screen-by-Screen UI Design & Analysis
1. Splash Screen
Purpose: Show logo briefly on app launch

UI Elements:

App logo (centered)

App name

Progress indicator or animation

🔧 Visual Style: Minimal, clean

2. Login / Register Screen
Purpose: Authenticate user with Room DB

UI Elements:

Username input (TextField)

Password input (TextField with hide/show toggle)

"Login" button

"Register" button or link

Error message or toast if failed

🔧 Visual Style: Card with inputs, bright button color (blue/green)

3. Home Dashboard Screen
Purpose: Show summary of total expenditure

UI Elements:

Greeting with user’s name

Cards showing:

Today’s Expense

This Month’s Expense

This Year’s Expense

Buttons:

Add Expense

Set Monthly Budget

View Reports

🔧 Visual Style: Dashboard tiles, modern, data-first look

4. Add Expense Screen
Purpose: Enter a new expense record

UI Elements:

Date picker (default today)

Amount (NumberField)

Category dropdown (Food, Travel, etc.)

Description (optional)

"Save" button

🔧 Visual Style: Clean form with input validation

5. Monthly Budget Screen
Purpose: Set limits per category

UI Elements:

List of categories

Input budget per category

Save button

Optionally: total monthly budget

🔧 Visual Style: Editable list with Save floating action button

6. Expense List Screen
Purpose: Show list of expenses by filter (Day/Month/Year)

UI Elements:

Filter chips (Daily / Monthly / Yearly)

List of expense items (date, amount, category, note)

Delete/Edit swipe actions

🔧 Visual Style: RecyclerView/ListView with icons

7. Reports/Graph Screen
Purpose: Visual representation of data

UI Elements:

Pie chart or bar graph

Filter dropdown (week, month, year)

Top 5 spending categories

Comparison with budget

🔧 Visual Style: Bright charts, easy to read

8. Profile/Settings Screen
Purpose: Manage user data

UI Elements:

Username/email

Change password

Reset data

Logout button

🔧 Visual Style: Profile card with basic settings

✅ Ready to Generate Images
I'll now create visual mockups of the following screens:

Splash Screen

Login / Register

Dashboard (Home)

Add Expense

Monthly Budget

Expense List

Reports

Profile

Let me start generating the UI image mockups.


ICONS:-

🟢 General Naming Convention
Use lowercase + underscores, e.g.:

pgsql
Copy
Edit
ic_login.xml
ic_food.png
📱 Splash / Login / Register Screen
Usage	Icon Name	Purpose
App Logo	ic_wallet_logo	Brand logo (main symbol)
Email Field	ic_email	Input hint icon
Password Field	ic_password	Input hint icon
Login Button	ic_login	Optional icon for button
Register Btn	ic_register	Optional icon for button
Show Password	ic_visibility	Toggle password visibility
Hide Password	ic_visibility_off	Toggle off

🏠 Dashboard (Home Screen)
Usage	Icon Name	Purpose
Daily Expense	ic_today	Show today's expense
Monthly Expense	ic_calendar_month	Monthly data summary
Yearly Expense	ic_calendar_year	Annual expense summary
Pie Chart	ic_pie_chart	Visual analytics
Add Expense	ic_add	FAB or toolbar icon
Reports	ic_bar_chart	Open report/chart view
Settings/Profile	ic_settings	Navigate to settings/profile

➕ Add Expense Screen
Usage	Icon Name	Purpose
Select Category	ic_category	Dropdown icon (optional)
Select Date	ic_calendar	Open date picker
Amount Field	ic_money	Input hint
Save Button	ic_save	Save new expense

💸 Expense Categories (Icons)
Category	Icon Name
Food	ic_food
Shopping	ic_shopping
Transport	ic_transport
Entertainment	ic_entertainment
Health/Medical	ic_health
Education	ic_education
Bills/Utilities	ic_bills
Travel	ic_travel
Others/Misc	ic_others

📊 Reports / Charts Screen
Usage	Icon Name
Bar Chart	ic_bar_chart
Pie Chart	ic_pie_chart
Filter	ic_filter_list
Back	ic_arrow_back

👤 Profile / Settings Screen
Usage	Icon Name
User Avatar	ic_user
Change Pass	ic_lock
Reset Data	ic_refresh
Logout	ic_logout
Language	ic_language
Theme Mode	ic_dark_mode or ic_light_mode

🗑️ List / Manage Expenses Screen
Usage	Icon Name
Edit Item	ic_edit
Delete Item	ic_delete
Swipe Left Icon	ic_swipe_delete
